                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10182" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2566</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">190 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">洞悉需求，破局垄断：玖谊源医用回旋加速器国产化替代进行时</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insight into Demand, Breaking Monopoly: Sichuan Longevous Beamtech Medical Cyclotron&#39;s Journey of Domestic Substitution</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马文聪，付森会，叶阳平，陈修德，吴小节</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川玖谊源粒子科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国产化替代；市场需求；自主研发；关键技术突破；医用回旋加速器</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Domestic Substitution, Market Demand, Independent R&amp;D, Key Technology Breakthrough, Medical Cyclotron</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本教学案例聚焦四川玖谊源粒子科技有限公司（简称玖谊源）如何在长期被国际巨头垄断的中国医用回旋加速器市场中，通过精准洞悉本土市场需求、实现关键核心技术突破，进而打破垄断，稳步推动国产化替代的进程。案例首先阐述了医用回旋加速器国产化替代的时代背景、国家战略及地方政策机遇，并分析了市场竞争格局。面对国际企业的技术壁垒和市场控制，玖谊源依托中国工程物理研究院的技术积淀，坚持自主研发，在核心技术领域取得突破，形成了差异化竞争优势。进一步从技术、组织、环境三个维度，深入剖析了玖谊源如何将技术创新与临床痛点和市场需求紧密结合。公司通过构建多层次产品线，满足基层医疗机构到顶尖科研单位的多样化需求，并积极布局售后服务网络和供应链生态。尽管面临挑战，玖谊源凭借其战略定位与市场开拓，已在国内市场取得显著进展，并成功实现产品出口。本案例旨在引导学生深入理解，本土后发企业在复杂市场环境中如何通过自主创新与精准市场定位，逐步实现高端医疗装备的国产化替代，以期打破国际垄断格局。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The teaching case focuses on how Sichuan Longevous Beamtech Co., Ltd., in the Chinese medical cyclotron market long monopolized by international giants, broke the monopoly and steadily promoted the process of domestic substitution by accurately understanding local market demand and achieving breakthroughs in key core technologies. The case first elaborates on the historical background of domestic substitution for medical cyclotrons, national strategies, and local policy opportunities, and analyzes the market competition landscape. Facing the technological barriers and market control of international enterprises, Longevous Beamtech, relying on the technological accumulation of the China Academy of Engineering Physics, insisted on independent research and development, achieved breakthroughs in core technology fields, and formed a differentiated competitive advantage. Furthermore, from the three dimensions of technology, organization, and environment (TOE), the case deeply analyzes how Longevous Beamtech closely integrated technological innovation with clinical pain points and market demands. The company meets the diverse needs of grassroots medical institutions to top-tier scientific research units by constructing a multi-level product line and actively lays out after-sales service networks and supply chain ecosystems. Despite facing challenges, Longevous Beamtech, has made significant progress in the domestic market and successfully exported its products through its strategic positioning and market development. This case aims to guide students to deeply understand how local latecomer enterprises can gradually achieve domestic substitution of high-end medical equipment through independent innovation and precise market positioning in a complex market environment, in order to break the international monopoly pattern.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国产化替代战略；TOE框架</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
